  7,42,Prout pro those believe lead righteous vita! - Nos nunquam burden any anima its means - these est dwellers Paradise. They abide it forever
  7,43,Nos remove totus jealousy their hearts Rivers flow them they dictus DEUS praised pro guiding nos! Nos possibly non guided non est DEUS guided nos. messengers noster Dominus perfecit bring truth. They est alias Hoc est tuus Paradise! Vos inherited it in return tuus works
  7,44,dwellers Paradise alias dwellers Hell Nos invenit noster Dominus promise est truth habet vos invenit tuus Dominus promise est truth They dictus Sic announcer them announce deus condemnation befallen transgressors
  7,45,Qui repel path DEUS strive factus it crooked regard Hereafter they est disbelievers
  7,46,barrier separates them dum Purgatory occupied people recognize each side their looks They alias dwellers de Paradise Pax est upon vos They non iniit (Paradise wishful thinking)
